just_use registry_generated.go

# label: GENERATED
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Hub that crudgen-compiled pages push into via init(). Each .claude → .go
file emits an init() calling registerGeneratedPage; GetPages() appends
generatedPages to the hardcoded list so nav / index / tour pick them up
automatically.

This removes the main.go / registry.go adjacency-churn that every new
CRUD page used to create. You don't edit this file when adding a page;
you add the .claude and let crudgen emit the init().
